        <h1 class="text-3xl text-[var(--color-3)] font-bold">Ch·ªçn s·∫£n ph·∫©m n·ªïi b·∫≠t (t·ªëi ƒëa 4)</h1>
        <input
          id="search-input"
          type="text"
          placeholder="üîç T√¨m theo t√™n s·∫£n ph·∫©m..."
